# Vercel only hosts the STATIC front-end (web/static). Exclude the Python backend
# and everything else so Vercel does not try to build it as a serverless function
# (which is what causes the "main.py does not define a top-level app" error).
# The backend (the alpha-beta API) runs on Render -- see render.yaml / README.
*.py
**/*.py
requirements*.txt
pyproject.toml
render.yaml
checkpoints/
notebooks/
tests/
docs/
assets/
logs/
pgn/
